messageBody:
Okay, I just changed the font. You can find it at:

http://quikscript.sourceforge.net/thoth.zip

Note that this is a different address than before. The site to which I
upload my font seems to have a glitch in which it does not replace an
old file with a new one. Since it is an open fonts site, I still wish to
put my font there, but in the meantime while I am trying to get this
problem straightened out, I'll keep a duplicate copy at sourceforge.

Paul
